  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/mlcompute\/mlclosstype\ncrawled: 2026-03-10T20:24:00Z\n---\n\n# MLCLossType\n\n**Enumeration**\n\nA loss function.\n\n## Declaration\n\n```swift\nenum MLCLossType\n```\n\n## Enumeration Cases\n\n- **MLCLossType.categoricalCrossEntropy**\n- **MLCLossType.cosineDistance**\n- **MLCLossType.hinge**\n- **MLCLossType.huber**\n- **MLCLossType.log**\n- **MLCLossType.meanAbsoluteError**\n- **MLCLossType.meanSquaredError**\n- **MLCLossType.sigmoidCrossEntropy**\n- **MLCLossType.softmaxCrossEntropy**\n- **debugDescription**: A textual description of the loss type, suitable for debugging.\n\n## Initializers\n\n- **init(rawValue:)**\n\n## Creating Loss Layers with Descriptors\n\n- **init(descriptor:)**: Creates a loss layer with the descriptor you specify.\n- **init(descriptor:weights:)**: Creates a loss layer with the descriptor and weights you specify.\n- **MLCLossDescriptor**: A configuration object you use to create a loss layer.\n\n## Conforms To\n\n- BitwiseCopyable\n- Equatable\n- Hashable\n- RawRepresentable\n- Sendable\n- SendableMetatype\n\n",
